<taxonomicName id="BA94A089A33765575E84FECE6996585E" authority="Hubner, 1825" authorityName="Hubner" authorityYear="1825" box="[1161,1432,330,357]" class="Insecta" family="Gelechiidae" genus="Hypatima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="501" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4FE00718A33765575E84FECE68F9585F" box="[1161,1271,331,356]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="501">Hypatima</emphasis>
Hübner, 1825
</taxonomicName>
. The generic assignment of the species needs to be appraised in the context of a revision.
</paragraph>
